; This is a helper function to check air pressure

(debug, Running helper function P501 for pressure checking)

o100 if [#<_pres_sense> EQ 1]
  M66 P[#<_tc_input_pres>] L4 Q0.01
  G4P0.1
  o101 while [#5399 EQ -1]
    G4P0
    (print, ATCI:0|Action Required|Insufficient air pressure, increase or supply compressed air to the spindle to continue.)
    G4P0
    M0
    M66 P[#<_tc_input_pres>] L4 Q0.01
    G4P0.1
  o101 endwhile
o100 endif

M99;